
<!-- ヒーローセクション -->
<div class="relative min-h-[100svh] bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/5 to-white overflow-hidden">
  <!-- メインビジュアル -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 min-h-[100svh] flex items-center relative z-10 pt-[4.5rem] lg:pt-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 w-full py-8 lg:py-20">
      <!-- テキストコンテンツ -->
      <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8 text-center lg:text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            あなたの肌ケア、<br>
            <span class="mt-2 sm:mt-3 lg:mt-4 inline-block">みんなで応援。</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-600">
            今日の努力は、明日の自信へ
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gray-600">
          毎日の肌ケアを記録して、<br class="sm:hidden">仲間と共に美肌への道を歩みましょう。<br class="hidden sm:block">
          あなたの努力を、みんなでサポートします。
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <%= link_to '新規登録して始める', new_user_path, class: 'w-full sm:w-auto sm:min-w-[240px] px-6 lg:px-8 py-3 lg:py-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-full hover:bg-primary/80 transition duration-300 text-sm lg:text-base font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center' %>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <%= link_to '掲示板を見てみる', boards_path, class: 'w-full sm:w-auto sm:min-w-[240px] px-6 lg:px-8 py-3 lg:py-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-full hover:bg-primary/80 transition duration-300 text-sm lg:text-base font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 特徴カード -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer" data-modal-target="skincare-modal" onclick="openModal('skincare-modal')">
          <div class="text-primary text-2xl mb-3 text-center">📝</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">スキンケアログ</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base">毎日の肌ケアを記録して、変化を実感</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer" data-modal-target="cheer-modal" onclick="openModal('cheer-modal')">
          <div class="text-primary text-2xl mb-3 text-center">❤️</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Cheer（いいね）機能</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base">仲間と応援し合って、モチベーション維持</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer" data-modal-target="trophy-modal" onclick="openModal('trophy-modal')">
          <div class="text-primary text-2xl mb-3 text-center">🏆</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">トロフィー</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base">達成感を可視化して、継続をサポート</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer" data-modal-target="calendar-modal" onclick="openModal('calendar-modal')">
          <div class="text-primary text-2xl mb-3 text-center">📅</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">継続記録</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base">日々の積み重ねを、確かな記録に</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- モーダル -->
  <div id="skincare-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 hidden items-center justify-center z-50">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl w-full mx-4 relative">
      <button onclick="closeModal('skincare-modal')" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">スキンケアログ機能について</h2>
      <div class="prose max-h-[70vh] overflow-y-auto">
        <p class="mb-4">スキンケアログ機能では、以下のことができます：</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>毎日のスキンケアルーティンを記録</li>
          <li>使用した製品や肌の状態をメモ</li>
          <li>写真で肌の変化を記録</li>
          <li>過去の記録を振り返り、効果を確認</li>
          <%= image_tag 'new_board.gif', style: 'width: 200px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-auto my-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg' %>
          <%= image_tag 'skin_care_log.gif', style: 'width: 200px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-auto my-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg' %>

        </ul>
        <p>継続的な記録により、あなたの肌ケアの効果を可視化します。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="cheer-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 hidden items-center justify-center z-50 overflow-y-auto">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl w-full mx-4 relative my-8">
      <button onclick="closeModal('cheer-modal')" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Cheer（いいね）機能について</h2>
      <div class="prose max-h-[70vh] overflow-y-auto">
        <!-- ここに詳細な説明を追加 -->
        <p>他のユーザーの投稿にCheer!を送ることができます。</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>他のユーザーの投稿にCheer!を送ってみんなのスキンケアを応援しましょう！</li>
          <li>（簡単に言うといいね機能です）</li>
          <%= image_tag 'cheer_movie.gif', style: 'width: 200px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-auto my-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg' %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="trophy-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 hidden items-center justify-center z-50">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl w-full mx-4 relative">
      <button onclick="closeModal('trophy-modal')" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">トロフィー機能について</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <!-- ここに詳細な説明を追加 -->
        <p>記録を継続していくと、トロフィーを獲得することができます。</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>手書きのトロフィーをいくつか用意しています！</li>
          <%= image_tag 'trophy_photo.png', style: 'width: 200px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-auto my-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg' %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="calendar-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 hidden items-center justify-center z-50">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl w-full mx-4 relative">
      <button onclick="closeModal('calendar-modal')" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">継続記録機能について</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <!-- ここに詳細な説明を追加 -->
        <p>継続記録の詳細を見ることができます</p>
        <p>自分の頑張りをチェックしよう！</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <%= image_tag 'streak_photo.png', style: 'width: 200px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-auto my-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg' %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 波形の装飾 -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 pointer-events-none z-[-1]">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" class="w-full h-auto" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path fill="hsl(var(--p) / 0.1)" fill-opacity="0.3" d="M0,96L48,112C96,128,192,160,288,160C384,160,480,128,576,122.7C672,117,768,139,864,154.7C960,171,1056,181,1152,165.3C1248,149,1344,107,1392,85.3L1440,64L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</div>
